Please have a look at http://code.google.com/p/pownce-jabber-bot/ for details
of installation and use.

For the moment, run "twistd -noy powncebot.tac" to start the bot.

Don't forget to set the settings in powncebot/settings.py

Dependencies:

"sqlalchemy==0.4.6"
"Twisted>=8.0.1"
"wokkel>=0.3.1"
"pownce-api"
"simplejson"


Cheers,
jezdez